                        <hr class="divider light my-4">
                        <p class="text-white-50 mb-4">HirePros listings hlep you search and choose from all the services and pros arround you and running in no time! Choose one or multiple of them, send them a requirement message and connect easily ! Hire them only if you like the deal!</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-light btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Login">Get Started!</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </body>

